  For email, registration costs 25DM
  For post, registration costs 30DM

 Send your appropriate registration fee (German money, EC-cheques or money
 transfer - bank:Raiffeisen-Volksbank Seiffen, bank code:87069075,
 account:421200) to:
         Beer Productions
         André + Ronny Beer
         Siedlung 6
         09548 Deutscheinsiedel
         Germany


