@node "History"
                            Development journal
                            ===================


                            ***  GeoWorld®  ***
                     © 1996 - 98 by Beer Productions



Version  Date      Remark
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1.0      Dec'1997  Version 1 of GeoWorld is officially released.

1.01     10/02/98  Following bugs were corrected:

                   ° Mistake in the Maxi-Search with a search on city names
                   ° Small balck lines when showing smaller maps
                   ° Incorrect display of 4 digit zip codes in the information
                     window
                   ° Inhabitants number going over edge of window resolved

                   Following functions were included:

                   ° More exact names of the regions in Great Britain (county
                     etc.)
                   ° Selection windows display better at minimum size
                   ° Selection windows show the number of matched countries /
                     cities

1.02     14/02/98  Following bugs were resolved:

                   ° Sometimes incorrect display of a country after selection
                     from the selection window
                   ° Display updated immediately after pressing mouse buttons
                   ° Selection of a continent / country on the map works if
                     started immediately (no title screen)

1.03     22/02/98  Following bugs were settled:

                   ° Program crashed with a search for a number term in the
                     Maxi-Search
                   ° Screen and window titles now displayed in selected font
                     and not Topaz 8
                   ° Screen title no longer changes when opening a new window
                     or during file access
                   ° File requester in the display window now remembers
                     correct directory

1.04     13/04/98  Following corrections/bugfixes were planned:

                   ° Change from a lot of small files to a few big files for
                     the city information
                   ° Changed the flag graphics (only 4 colours possible until
                     now)
                   ° Bug fixed in keyboard control

1.05     10/05/98  Following corrections/bugfixes were planned:

                   ° Elimination of a bug in the menu control of the cities
                     information window
                   ° Included Austrian and Swiss zip codes
                   ° Removed the time limitation of 15 minutes in the demo
                     version
                   ° Removed bug in the picture save requester

1.06     17/05/98  Following adjustments/bug fixes were made:

                   ° Enlargment of the data buffers in preparation for more
                     information
                   ° Removal of an error in the listview window of the
                     countries information, after selecting "Print all"
                   ° Adjusted load routine for city information

1.07     18/08/98  Following adjustments/bug fixes were made:

                   ° Two identical answers in the GeoWorld quiz was resolved
                   ° Inclusion of the currencies in the GeoWorld quiz
                   ° Number of questions in the GeoWorld quiz expandable at
                     will
                   ° Possibility to save maps (with drawn cities) for use at
                     at later time
                   ° Better operation of the selection windows, now scroll
                     while the mouse button is pressed
                   ° Inclusion of a "Not" search in the Maxi-Search (items
                     match if they do not match the entered fields)

1.08     13/09/98  Following adjustments/bug fixes were made:

                   ° Added Alaska and Hawaii into the USA map
                   ° Added Canaries into the Spanish map
                   ° Country data now includes Gross National Product (GNP)
                     as a total and per head of population
                   ° Expanded the sorting and searching functions to include
                     the two above additions
                   ° Bug fixed in the state and set files
                   ° Overworked the map of the world - more precise retreival
                     of data from mouse clicks
                   ° Overworked some continents - each point bigger than 1
                     pixel responds immediately to a mouse click
                   ° Removal of a bug in the "Show city" function
                   ° Free memory is checked at start of program (at least 2.5Mb
                     RAM as well as 900kb Chip RAM)
                   ° New (improved) maps for Haiti and the Dominican Republic
                     as well as for Ecuador including the Galapogan Islands
                   ° Shortening of city names in the information window, in the
                     quiz and the map (text in brackets and after slashes is
                     left out)

1.09     04/11/98  Following adjustments/bug fixes were made:

                   ° Check for the presence of a second GeoWorld task at start
                     of program
                   ° Enhancement of the print function with the possibility to
                     copy data to the clipboard
                   ° Different display times for right and wrong answers
                     in the GeoWorld quiz
                   ° Added a new selection window for international
                     organizations in the main window
                   ° Changed menus to GadTools menus and removed a bug
                     with the setting of the sorting direction
                   ° Expansion of the countries data by including the country
                     name in its native language
                   ° Improved searching capability while searching for country
                     or city names (you can search for name in short form, in
                     detailed name and name in native language)
                   ° Searching for umlauts and special characters (ä,ö,ü,á
                     etc.) is now possible in all search functions of GeoWorld
                   ° Integration of a progress bar while search is in progress
                     in the Maxi-Search (de-activation is possible)
                   ° Better font sensitivity in the country and city
                     information windows
                   ° Adaption of the "About" requester to British and American
                     postal adresses
                   ° Removal of a bug during display of non-numeric holidays
                     (e.g. "first Sunday in June")
                   ° Added currency information to the main menu, from the
                     control window
@endnode

